  "prompt": "What is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Treutlen County GA?",
  "response": "If you're looking for an inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Treutlen County, Georgia, you may want to consider centers in nearby cities as well. Here are a few options that could be suitable, though it's important to contact them directly to confirm if they meet your specific needs:\n\n1. **Willingway** - Located in Statesboro, GA, Willingway specializes in the treatment of alcohol and drug addiction with a variety of programs including inpatient services.\n\n2. **Pineland BHDD** - Also located in Statesboro, GA, Pineland Behavioral Health Developmental Disabilities offers a range of addiction treatment services.\n\n3. **Twin Lakes Recovery Center** - Located a bit further away in Monroe, GA, it provides comprehensive treatment programs including detox, residential treatment, and aftercare.\n\n4. **Ridgeview Institute** - Located in Smyrna, GA, Ridgeview offers a variety of programs for addiction and mental health issues, including inpatient care.\n\nBefore deciding, consider factors such as the specific services offered, treatment approaches, insurance acceptance, and accreditation. It's also helpful to visit facilities if possible, or schedule a consultation to determine which center best meets your needs.",
